All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Runnable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, javax.swing.RootPaneContainer, javax.swing.WindowConstants
public class LatexPrerenderer
extends InterruptableProgressDialog

This object renders all labels in a DES model and displays the progress in a dialog box with a progress bar. The rendering can be interrupted by the user.

The intended use is when loading a file or when turning on LaTeX rendering for the labels.

Author:
Lenko Grigorov
